annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L7; Binds to G-rich structures in 28S rRNA and in mRNAs. Plays a regulatory role in the translation apparatus; inhibits cell-free translation of mRNAs (By similarity)
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S25; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: translation; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eS25 family
